10 foils of enriched 235U (total mass of ~113 mg)
deposited on both sides of Ti foil (4 cm diam, 3 um
FIGARO neutron detector array for prompt
17 Eljen EJ301 organic liquid scintillators (613.6 cm3,
12.5 cm in diam., 5.0 cm in depth for each).
~1 m away from the center of the target position
yielding an angular coverage from 42 to 125 deg in
Only six detectors with the best pulse-height
distributions were chosen for the analysis.
